     2→/**
     3→ * MMS Demo Data Generator CLI
     4→ *
     5→ * Usage:
     6→ *   bun run src/demo/cli.ts [options]
     7→ *
     8→ * Options:
     9→ *   --trains <number>     Number of trains to generate (default: 128)
    10→ *   --history <years>     Years of historical data (default: 5)
